ittee, Ligue de Football Professionnel, and several French art organizations.\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 852, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 628, \"end\": 635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing\", \"score\": 0.9999802087030182, \"rank\": 1.979167074926291e-05, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing\"}, {\"begin\": 639, \"end\": 644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999974365892, \"rank\": 2.563339699354637e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 662, \"end\": 669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.8358311269006183, \"rank\": 0.16864703220380498, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 674, \"end\": 680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9848226127450252, \"rank\": 0.015056974909351937, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 707, \"end\": 724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"China Media Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 726, \"end\": 729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 0.9985364210806513, \"rank\": 0.0014657198295825176, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_